{"article_id":"pBKeXmS3TMY2CsLw","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"( CNN )","depth":3},{"id":1,"text":"Just days after insisting","depth":6},{"id":2,"text":"that any spending bill","depth":8},{"id":3,"text":"to keep the federal government open","depth":8},{"id":4,"text":"include more than $ 1 billion for his proposed border wall ,","depth":7},{"id":5,"text":"President Trump backed off that pledge","depth":6},{"id":6,"text":"-- abruptly ending the expected brinksmanship between the White House and Congress","depth":7},{"id":7,"text":"expected to dominate the week .","depth":7},{"id":8,"text":"`` Not this week , ''","depth":6},{"id":9,"text":"White House counselor Kellyanne Conway said of the push for $ 1.4 billion as a downpayment for the border wall in a Tuesday morning interview with Fox News .","depth":6},{"id":10,"text":"`` Building that wall","depth":8},{"id":11,"text":"and having it funded remains an important priority to him , ''","depth":8},{"id":12,"text":"she added .","depth":7},{"id":13,"text":"`` We also know","depth":7},{"id":14,"text":"that that can happen later this year and into next year . ''","depth":7},{"id":15,"text":"That rapid cycle of demand-to-capitulation is enough","depth":4},{"id":16,"text":"to give you whiplash .","depth":4},{"id":17,"text":"But wait !","depth":5},{"id":18,"text":"There 's more !","depth":5},{"id":19,"text":"Trump tweeted Tuesday","depth":8},{"id":20,"text":"that his changed position was n't a change at all ,","depth":8},{"id":21,"text":"but that ignores the fact","depth":8},{"id":22,"text":"that he demanded something","depth":9},{"id":23,"text":"that now wo n't be in the spending bill .","depth":9},{"id":24,"text":"Do n't let the fake media tell you","depth":8},{"id":25,"text":"that I have changed my position on the WALL .","depth":8},{"id":26,"text":"It will get built","depth":9},{"id":27,"text":"and help stop drugs , human trafficking etc .","depth":9},{"id":28,"text":"Or will it ?","depth":8},{"id":29,"text":"A White House official told CNN 's Jim Acosta","depth":6},{"id":30,"text":"that Trump expects money for the border wall to be included in the bill this week .","depth":6},{"id":31,"text":"The simple political fact is that a government shutdown would be a massive political problem for Republicans .","depth":5},{"id":32,"text":"They control both chambers of Congress and the White House","depth":6},{"id":33,"text":"-- and everyone knows it .","depth":6},{"id":34,"text":"Blaming Democrats for their intransigence would be a non-starter in such a situation .","depth":5},{"id":35,"text":"The full weight of the blame would fall on Republicans","depth":7},{"id":36,"text":"-- particularly Congressional Republicans ,","depth":8},{"id":37,"text":"many of whom have to stand for re-election in 18 months time .","depth":8},{"id":38,"text":"Republicans are still struggling to prove to a skeptical public","depth":7},{"id":39,"text":"that they can be a governing party","depth":8},{"id":40,"text":"not just the loyal opposition .","depth":8},{"id":41,"text":"Shutting down the government for even a day would be proof point # 1 for Democrats","depth":5},{"id":42,"text":"to make the argument","depth":6},{"id":43,"text":"that Republicans are unsuited to lead .","depth":6},{"id":44,"text":"And doing so over a border wall proposal","depth":5},{"id":45,"text":"that 's not popular outside a portion of the Republican base would be even more disastrous .","depth":5},{"id":46,"text":"Trump , unlike , say , Ted Cruz , is not the sort of person","depth":5},{"id":47,"text":"to charge at political windmills .","depth":5},{"id":48,"text":"He wants to win , first and foremost .","depth":5},{"id":49,"text":"And the way","depth":7},{"id":50,"text":"to win","depth":7},{"id":51,"text":"is to pick fights","depth":7},{"id":52,"text":"where success is the very likely outcome .","depth":7},{"id":53,"text":"Trump punted","depth":7},{"id":54,"text":"because punting made political sense .","depth":7},{"id":55,"text":"His potential reversal on punting may be an attempt","depth":8},{"id":56,"text":"to save some face","depth":8},{"id":57,"text":"-- perhaps by extracting a smaller amount of money","depth":8},{"id":58,"text":"to be included in the bill","depth":9},{"id":59,"text":"to fund some portion of the wall .","depth":9},{"id":60,"text":"What 's more baffling to me is why he floated the $ 1.4 billion allocation for the border wall in the first place .","depth":6},{"id":61,"text":"Was it a trial balloon","depth":8},{"id":62,"text":"to see","depth":9},{"id":63,"text":"if Congressional Republicans might be open to it ?","depth":9},{"id":64,"text":"An attempt to work the refs a bit","depth":9},{"id":65,"text":"so","depth":10},{"id":66,"text":"when the next spending debate comes up","depth":11},{"id":67,"text":"Trump has set the floor of what he wants to see spent on the wall ?","depth":11},{"id":68,"text":"Or was it just something","depth":9},{"id":69,"text":"Trump said one day","depth":10},{"id":70,"text":"and then quickly realized was going nowhere ?","depth":10},{"id":71,"text":"With Trump the line between strategy and sounding-off is a fuzzy one .","depth":5},{"id":72,"text":"But ,","depth":7},{"id":73,"text":"regardless of his reasoning ,","depth":8},{"id":74,"text":"Trump blinked","depth":10},{"id":75,"text":"-- and blinked quickly --","depth":10},{"id":76,"text":"in his second major showdown with a Republican Congress .","depth":9},{"id":77,"text":"Worth noting :","depth":7},{"id":78,"text":"He also blinked the first time ,","depth":8},{"id":79,"text":"telling Speaker Paul Ryan to pull the healthcare bill","depth":9},{"id":80,"text":"before it even came to a vote .","depth":9}],"relations":[{"parent":161,"left":111,"right":160,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":111,"left":95,"right":110,"relation":"evaluation","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":95,"left":0,"right":94,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":94,"left":87,"right":93,"relation":"elaboration","nucle